/>\neven流行歌最重要最搵錢係個hook, 個hook其實咪又係講緊個好catchy既曲 我理得你填咩詞落去 你wu wu wu都得架<br />\n<br />\n冇曲得詞, 呢個就叫詞 而唔係歌 又點會詞反客為主大得過曲?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n無乜編曲？<br />\n你聽清唱囉..."},{"pid":"8ec1b4e59c57dc353ad139a92f0b921786145664","tid":244314,"uid":103207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T04:01:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cSDZI9GCLII\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcSDZI9GCLII&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=e78c0b09\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cSDZI9GCLII</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bB1kikWPM8s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbB1kikWPM8s&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=d5d47839\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bB1kikWPM8s</a><br />\n<br />\n詞既重要性真係比唔上曲+唱者把聲同唱功重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6abde40148de3073656937f9d84be2912d75c0","tid":244314,"uid":550,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T04:11:00.000Z","msg":"曲<br />\n廣東歌最大問題係詞大過曲<br />\n令到傳播出去有好大難度<br />\n外國人唔會理解你歌詞意思<br />\nKpop啲歌詞都係9up但個melody夠勁<br />\n先可以全球風靡"},{"pid":"68bb305378542997e1f3fb654e1025cf192c0729","tid":244314,"uid":13628,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T04:23:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cSDZI9GCLII\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DcSDZI9GCLII&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=e78c0b09\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=cSDZI9GCLII</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bB1kikWPM8s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DbB1kikWPM8s&d=RGPktlJYpqjIeXpZRAkgw%2F755KD0hvcRsprRlRVhNBc%3D&h=d5d47839\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=bB1kikWPM8s</a><br />\n<br />\n詞既重要性真係比唔上曲+唱者把聲同唱功重要<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n第一首 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"75195c964318c37172c7c29d1c2bb491722a5da4","tid":244314,"uid":89282,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T05:28:53.000Z","msg":"請問攞廣東歌黎講有咩意義?廣東歌 are just a shit.兩樣野佢都冇,係都唔攞黎做例子啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"451f5d6a35f5d8f769d16cb3f336c98fb6223fcd","tid":244314,"uid":115078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T05:34:07.000Z","msg":"歌重要啲 古典樂純音樂都可以帶到感情出黎 不過有埋詞加深/改變歌嘅感情<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"80689c6e2a926a5195617186cf887bea8c4354aa","tid":244314,"uid":353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T05:47:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>詞!!!!<br />\n如果要稱一首歌係藝術<br />\n就一定要表達到一個情感或者表達到一個作者嘅意思<br />\n但如果一首歌連詞都尻填又點稱得上係藝術<br />\n極其量只可以話係商品<br />\n但一首曲差但係詞有心思嘅<br />\n都可以話係一個藝術品<br />\n不過只係質素差啲咁解<br />\n<br />\n一首流行歌嘅曲本身係無意義<br />\n係詞賦予佢意思比人寄託<br />\n但一首詞就算無曲<br />\n都可以表達到作者嘅意思<br />\n係表達方式無咁好姐<br />\n<br />\n我知大家對歌係咪藝術嘅定義都唔同<br />\n不過我覺得如果對歌係講究嘅<br />\n就一定會著重詞多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淨係聽POP既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"946fc335509310a991909b22e995b4ea336eb59f","tid":244314,"uid":20654,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T05:56:29.000Z","msg":"編曲先最緊要<br />\n編先係真係比個idea生命"},{"pid":"f4531d8e2fa90a116841fb762296e2d9688adfaf","tid":244314,"uid":56388,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-18T06:01:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>詞!!!!<br />\n如果要稱一首歌係藝術<br />\n就一定要表達到一個情感或者表達到一個作者嘅意思<br />\n但如果一首歌連詞都尻填又點稱得上係藝術<br />\n極其量只可以話係商品<br />\n但一首曲差但係詞有心思嘅<br />\n都可以話係一個藝術品<br />\n不過只係質素差啲咁解<br />\n<br />\n一首流行歌嘅曲本身係無意義<br />\n係詞賦予佢意思比人寄託<br />\n但一首詞就算無曲<br />\n都可以表達到作者嘅意思<br />\n係表達方式無咁好姐<br />\n<br />\n我知大家對歌係咪藝術嘅定義都唔同<br />\n不過我覺得如果對歌係講究嘅<br />\n就一定會著重詞多啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n淨係聽POP既人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n所以廣東流行曲嘅作曲編曲千篇一律唔係冇原因<br />\n啲 producer 會覺得：既然你地都唔重視作曲編曲，咁我地仲喺呢方面落力嚟做乜嘢？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n結果就係機械式melody同廿年不變嘅鋼琴-&gt;鼓Bass弦樂編曲<br />\n咁食開詞大嘅 canton-pop 聽眾鐘意呢味嘅就冇乜問題，<br />\n但係背後就係流失咗好多人去聽其他嘢<br />\n咁我覺得百貨應百客，冇乜問題嘅，但係唔好再問我地點解唔支持本地流行樂<br />\n（我係要聽本土嘅都都聽indie嘢啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"}]}